      • getPosition

        long getPosition()
                 throws IOException
        Returns offset of next byte to be returned by a read method.
        Returns:
        offset of next byte which will be returned with next SequentialRead.read() (if no more bytes are left it returns a value >= length of source)
        Throws:
        IOException
